@adminToken = paste-admin-jwt-here
@itemId = paste-item-id-here

### Get analytics
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/analytics
Authorization: BEARER {{adminToken}}

###

### Get flagged reports
GET http://localhost:5000/api/admin/reports
Authorization: BEARER {{adminToken}}

###

### Remove a listing
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/admin/reports/{{itemId}}/remove
Authorization: BEARER {{adminToken}}

###

### Flag an item (any logged in user)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/admin/flag/{{itemId}}
Authorization: BEARER {{adminToken}}
